extendedInfo.description: 1. From MSRP, Base Capital Cost, Additional Lease Cost, Down payment, Trade-in-Credit, Other reductions, Residual value ($ or %), Money Factor (absolute or %), lease term, sales tax calculate lease payment2. When lease payment is provided calculate money factor and interest rate3. Shows summary/detail4. Save and email

reviews.title: Does Account For Location
reviews.comment: Do not use if you want to have an accurate lease calculation.  The app does not help you with regional calculations!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Works perfectly
reviews.comment: This app works perfectly. Car leasing is figured the same way in Cali as it is in FLORIDA or anywhere else. I have no idea what \"regional\" crap the previous reviewer is talking about.
reviews.author: Robert Boehme
